{"tag":"section","attrib":{"id":"idbf5c9632-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s12007"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"12007"},"text":"§ 12007.","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" No antitrust immunity or defenses","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Nothing in this chapter shall be deemed to convey to any person, partnership, corporation, or other entity immunity from civil or criminal liability under any antitrust law or to create defenses to actions under any antitrust law. As used in this section, “antitrust laws” means those Acts set forth in ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t15/s12"},"text":"section 12 of title 15","children":[],"tail":"."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":null},{"tag":"sourceCredit","attrib":{"id":"idbf5c9633-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa"},"text":"(","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/101/218/s10"},"text":"Pub. L. 101–218, § 10","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1989-12-11"},"text":"Dec. 11, 1989","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/103/1869"},"text":"103 Stat. 1869","children":[],"tail":".)"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"notes","attrib":{"type":"uscNote","id":"idbf5c9634-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"note","attrib":{"role":"crossHeading","topic":"editorialNotes","id":"idbf5c9635-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"b","attrib":{},"text":"Editorial Notes","children":[],"tail":null}],"tail":null}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"referencesInText","id":"idbf5c9636-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"References in Text","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"This chapter, referred to in text, was in the original “this Act”, meaning ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/101/218"},"text":"Pub. L. 101–218","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1989-12-11"},"text":"Dec. 11, 1989","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/103/1859"},"text":"103 Stat. 1859","children":[],"tail":", known as the Renewable Energy and Energy Efficiency Technology Competitiveness Act of 1989, which is classified principally to this chapter. For complete classification of this Act to the Code, see Short Title note set out under "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t42/s12001"},"text":"section 12001 of this title","children":[],"tail":" and Tables."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":null}
